---
question: Are period pills safe?
es:
  question: ¿Son seguras las píldoras menstruales?
  __question: AXk0/9wlSCdOwX49CEg+LkNOgG7Wu+HB76T+x3GWtGA=

---

Yes. These pills have been used for decades and are [safe](https://www.reproductiveaccess.org/resource/insights-period-pills). They cause bleeding and cramping, but these are expected effects of the medications and indicate that they are working.
